## Security & Secrets
- Never hardcode API keys, PATs, OAuth tokens. Use env vars + `.env.example`.
- Never pass credentials as inline env vars in Bash commands.
- Never commit `.env`, `.claude/settings.local.json`, `.mcp.json`, credentials files.
- RBAC / auth checks on all mutating endpoints (universal § 30.2).
- Redact PII + secrets at capture time (universal § 23).
- [ADD PROJECT-SPECIFIC SECURITY RULES]

